install TF2_tools

To install `tf2_tools` on Ubuntu with ROS 2 Iron, follow these steps:

1. Open a terminal.

2. Update your package lists:
   ```
   sudo apt update
   ```

3. Install `tf2_tools`:
   ```
   sudo apt install ros-iron-tf2-tools
   ```

This will install `tf2_tools` and any dependencies it might need. After installation, you can use the tools included in the `tf2_tools` package.